name: Deluxe King Room
description: A spacious Deluxe King Room featuring a luxurious king-size bed dressed in fine linens, elegant decor, and an ensuite bathroom with complimentary toiletries. This room is perfect for a relaxing stay, offering amenities such as a flat-screen TV, mini-fridge, and coffee maker. Guests can enjoy stunning views of the surrounding area from the large windows, making it ideal for couples or those seeking a bit of indulgence.

name: Single Room
description: A cozy Single Room designed for solo travelers, offering a comfortable single bed with plush bedding, free Wi-Fi, and a compact work desk. The room is well-appointed with modern decor and comes with a private bathroom featuring a walk-in shower. Ideal for short stays, this room provides a peaceful retreat while being conveniently located near hotel amenities.

name: Twin Room
description: This modern Twin Room features two separate twin beds, perfect for friends or colleagues traveling together. The room includes an ensuite bathroom, free toiletries, and a cozy seating area. Guests can enjoy a flat-screen TV and complimentary Wi-Fi, making it a comfortable and convenient choice for both leisure and business trips.

name: Standard Double Room
description: A cozy Standard Double Room featuring a comfortable queen-sized bed, elegant furnishings, and an ensuite bathroom. The room is equipped with a flat-screen TV, coffee maker, and complimentary Wi-Fi. Ideal for couples or individuals looking for a charming and affordable stay, this room combines comfort with convenience, allowing guests to relax after a busy day exploring the area.

name: Superior Double Room
description: Bright and spacious, the Superior Double Room boasts a double bed with stylish furnishings and a stunning view of the city. The room features a seating area, flat-screen TV, and a well-appointed bathroom with premium toiletries. This room is perfect for guests who want a bit more space and comfort during their stay, ensuring a delightful experience for both business and leisure travelers.

name: Family Suite
description: An ideal Family Suite designed for families, offering a king-sized bed and a comfortable sofa bed. The suite features a large living space, kitchenette, and a balcony with scenic views. Equipped with family-friendly amenities, including a flat-screen TV and games, this suite ensures a fun and memorable stay for families looking to enjoy their time together in comfort.

name: Executive Suite
description: Experience luxury in our Executive Suite, which features a king-sized bed, separate living area, and a private balcony. Enjoy a mini-bar stocked with refreshments and premium toiletries in the spacious bathroom. Perfect for business travelers, this suite offers a serene environment, high-speed internet access, and elegant decor, making it an ideal choice for those seeking comfort and sophistication.

name: Business Class Room
description: Our Business Class Room is designed for the corporate traveler, equipped with a comfortable bed, high-speed internet, and a large work desk. Guests can enjoy access to a business lounge and meeting facilities. The room is modern and well-appointed, ensuring a productive stay while providing all the comforts of home for relaxation at the end of a busy day.

name: Presidential Suite
description: The Presidential Suite offers the pinnacle of luxury, featuring a king-sized bed, a private terrace with breathtaking views, and a spacious living room. The elegant bathroom includes a jacuzzi for ultimate relaxation. With butler service and high-end amenities, this suite is perfect for those looking for an exceptional and indulgent experience during their stay.

name: Junior Suite
description: Our spacious Junior Suite offers a king-sized bed, a cozy sitting area, and a private balcony. Equipped with luxury amenities and a modern bathroom, this suite provides a perfect blend of comfort and style. Ideal for couples or individuals seeking a romantic getaway, the Junior Suite ensures a delightful experience in a tranquil setting.

name: Basic Single Room
description: A practical Basic Single Room designed for budget-conscious travelers. This room features a comfortable single bed, an en-suite bathroom, and free Wi-Fi. With essential amenities, this cozy space is perfect for those seeking a simple yet comfortable stay, making it an excellent choice for short visits.

name: Panoramic Room
description: Enjoy breathtaking views in our Panoramic Room, which features floor-to-ceiling windows and a queen-sized bed. This well-appointed room includes a work desk, free Wi-Fi, and a stylish bathroom with premium amenities. Ideal for both business and leisure travelers, this room combines comfort with stunning surroundings for a memorable stay.

name: Luxury King Suite
description: The Luxury King Suite is a premium choice featuring a spacious layout with a king-sized bed and a separate living area. Guests can enjoy modern amenities, including a large flat-screen TV and a luxurious bathroom with a rainfall shower. This suite is ideal for those seeking comfort and elegance, providing a relaxing retreat after a busy day.

name: Standard Family Room
description: A family-friendly Standard Family Room featuring two double beds, a cozy TV area, and a mini-fridge. Ideal for family getaways, this room is equipped with everything needed for a comfortable stay, including a spacious bathroom. Located conveniently near hotel amenities, this room ensures a delightful experience for guests of all ages.

name: Eco-Friendly Room
description: Our Eco-Friendly Room is designed with sustainability in mind, featuring a queen bed, energy-efficient appliances, and eco-friendly toiletries. This room provides a cozy atmosphere while promoting responsible travel. Perfect for green travelers, it offers all the modern comforts without compromising on style or comfort.

name: Compact Double Room
description: A compact yet comfortable Double Room featuring a double bed, essential amenities, and an ensuite bathroom. This room is perfect for those seeking a budget-friendly option while still enjoying a relaxing environment. Ideal for short stays, it provides guests with everything they need for a pleasant visit.

name: Romantic Suite
description: Create lasting memories in our Romantic Suite, designed for couples. This suite features a king-sized bed, soft ambient lighting, and a luxurious jacuzzi. Perfect for special occasions, it offers an intimate setting with exquisite decor and all the amenities needed for a romantic getaway.

name: Corner Suite
description: The Corner Suite offers panoramic views and a king-sized bed, alongside a spacious living area and modern decor. Guests can relax on their private balcony while enjoying the beautiful scenery. Perfect for extended stays, this suite provides all the comforts of home with a touch of luxury.

name: Classic Room
description: The Classic Room features elegant decor with a queen-sized bed and a marble bathroom. Equipped with a flat-screen TV and a mini-bar, this room combines timeless style with modern amenities. Ideal for those looking for a charming retreat, it offers comfort and sophistication for an enjoyable stay.

name: Standard Twin Room
description: Our Standard Twin Room provides cozy accommodations with two single beds, a private bathroom, and a work desk. Perfect for friends or family, this room is designed for comfort while being conveniently located near all hotel amenities, ensuring a pleasant and enjoyable stay.

name: Single Economy Room
description: The Single Economy Room is a budget-friendly option featuring a single bed, an en-suite bathroom, and free Wi-Fi. Suitable for solo travelers looking for a comfortable yet affordable stay, this room provides all the essential amenities needed for a cozy retreat during short visits.

name: Cozy Double Room
description: A warm and inviting Cozy Double Room with a double bed and modern decor. Ideal for couples or solo travelers on a weekend trip, it features essential amenities and free Wi-Fi, ensuring a pleasant stay with all the comforts of home.

name: Superior King Room
description: The Superior King Room offers extra space with a luxurious king-sized bed, modern furnishings, and a large ensuite bathroom. Perfect for longer stays, this room provides comfort and style, ensuring that guests feel relaxed and at home during their visit.

name: Luxury Family Suite
description: Our Luxury Family Suite features two bedrooms, a spacious living room, and a fully equipped kitchenette. Designed for families, this suite provides ample space and comfort, making it ideal for longer stays while allowing everyone to enjoy their time together in style.

name: Economy Twin Room
description: The Economy Twin Room is a simple and affordable option featuring two single beds, free Wi-Fi, and access to a shared bathroom. Ideal for budget travelers, this cozy room provides a comfortable place to rest after a day of exploring.

name: Comfort Double Room
description: Our Comfort Double Room is designed for a relaxing stay, featuring a queen-sized bed, a cozy seating area, and modern decor. With complimentary coffee and tea, this room ensures that guests have everything they need for a delightful and restful visit.

name: Suite with City View
description: The Suite with City View offers breathtaking sights of the city skyline, featuring a king-sized bed, a separate living room, and a luxurious marble bathroom. This suite is perfect for those seeking an upscale experience while enjoying the vibrant atmosphere of the city from the comfort of their room.

name: Basic Twin Room
description: Our Basic Twin Room provides a no-frills option with two twin beds, a TV, and a shared bathroom. Suitable for short stays or budget travelers, this room is designed to offer a comfortable place to unwind without compromising on value.

name: Luxury Executive Suite
description: The Luxury Executive Suite features exclusive amenities including a spacious living area, a king-sized bed, and access to the executive lounge. Ideal for business travelers, this suite offers a combination of comfort and luxury to ensure a productive and enjoyable stay.

name: Premier Family Room
description: A spacious Premier Family Room featuring two double beds, a dining area, and a kitchenette. Perfect for families looking for extra comfort and convenience, this room provides a relaxing atmosphere while being conveniently located near attractions and hotel amenities.
